description: Penny Play loves role playing. In scene one, poor Penny the warehouse worker, is attacked by a nailgun weilding bad guy and stapled into suspension by her coveralls! Lovely Penny is tough, sexy and lots of fun, as she is told to resist me as much as possible in the scene four barrel dunking scene. Was she successful in resisting me? No, but it sure is fun to watch her try. Love ya Penny. Come back and Play again sometime.
title: Penny Barber
